snippet.title: sin(e)s - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now: https://future-reality-softworks.itch.io/sines

sin(e)s is an interactive piece of software presented by the Seismic Safety Commission - SSc.
It simulates the events of a catastrophic earthquake and aims to prepare the trainees for any and all events following a seismic event.

Remember: 
Your senses can and will deceive you. Seemingly normal 
occurrences can prove to be fatal. 

A game made by:
pastasfuture: https://twitter.com/pastasfuture
Neurobew: https://twitter.com/Neurobew

Music by: 
Viktor Kraus: https://twitter.com/ViktorKraus2
